body:
Hello again forum. thanks for hearing all my questions as I learn to use ladybug and honeybee. 



On the building program component there is primary school and secondary school but no listing for college??? Is it possible to add this? Where are these programs pulled from? Thank you. Ethan

replies.body:
They are coming from OpenStudio's templates. You can create your own template but it won't be easy. If you have a template for collage in EnergyPlus you can assign them to your zones (change the default schedules and loads.)

Mostapha
